Subject: Re: [T2] alternator

I recommend running the "Exhaust Elbow".  This where HOT air exits
from the back of the alternator.  Fresh air (cooler, relatively
speaking) goes into the front (pulley) side of the alternator.  Better
to be safe than sorry IMHO
